  "description": {
    "en": "Herbal preparation derived from Jinyinhua. Known in English as honeysuckle, jinyinhua is a sweet and cooling herb that enters the lung, stomach and large intestine meridians. It is used to clear heat, relieve the body of toxins and expel wind ..."
